title: Outside the Office
description: It's 2AM. You find yourself standing in the parking lot of an office building. The lights are bright and cold. You spot something shiny under Cherine's car...
unlock_description: Oh no, it's Douglas... 'Hey man are looking for Cherine's key I found this key over by the smoke stack but I don't know they belong to maybe they're-' You stop listening to him and take the key...
